Transcription.Text: His American bosses, 20th- Century Fox, have recently given Frankie the full, razzamataz, red-carpet treatment. But they haven't done a thing for his film carreer that Anna Neagle and Herbert Wilcox were not doing better here, before the platinum-plated Hollywood carrot was dangled before his nose.
